org.apache.activemq.core.server.group.impl

Class RemoteGroupingHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.activemq.core.server.group.impl.GroupHandlingAbstract
      • org.apache.activemq.core.server.group.impl.RemoteGroupingHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.activemq.core.server.ActiveMQComponent, GroupingHandler, org.apache.activemq.core.server.management.NotificationListener

    public final class RemoteGroupingHandler
extends GroupHandlingAbstract
    A remote Grouping handler.

    This will use management notifications to communicate with the node that has the Local Grouping handler to make proposals.

    Author:
    Andy Taylor
